        <abstract> 
<p>Proposes to delay issue [of 4th ed. of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>] until November to obtain better market conditions. Now printing 1250 copies.</p> 
            <p>Explains practice of not cutting pages is due to propensity of English public to read books without buying them.</p>
